# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Environment Variables for vac811
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Copy this file to .env.production and .env.preview, then fill in the values.
# These files are NOT committed to git (see .gitignore).
# Wrangler loads them automatically when deploying.

# ─── API Keys & Authentication ───────────────────────────────────────────────

# Anthropic Claude API key (for gallery curation AI scoring)
# Get it from: https://console.anthropic.com/keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# OpenAI API key (for gallery preflight gpt-4o-mini scoring)
# Get it from: https://platform.openai.com/account/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# Google APIs (for Drive access to photo library)
# See docs/google-sso-setup.md for full setup instructions
GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_KEY={"type":"service_account","project_id":"...","private_key":"..."}
GOOGLE_DRIVE_FOLDER_ID=1abc...

# Instagram sync credentials (60-day rotating token)
# See docs/instagram-sync-setup.md for refresh instructions
INSTAGRAM_SYNC_ENDPOINT=https://graph.instagram.com/...
INSTAGRAM_SYNC_TOKEN=IGQVJWe...

# ECSET authentication (Hungarian scout roster system)
# Contact the ECSET administrator for credentials
ECSET_USERNAME=...
ECSET_PASSWORD=...
ECSET_TOTP_SECRET=...

# ─── Build-time Variables (VITE_* for client-side) ──────────────────────────

# Google OAuth client ID for sign-in
# From: Google Cloud Console → Credentials → OAuth 2.0 Client IDs
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=...apps.googleusercontent.com

# Proxy service for Google Drive (image proxy worker)
# This is the deployed google-git-proxy worker URL
VITE_PROXY_URL=https://google-git-proxy.vac811.workers.dev

# Image CDN URL (Cloudflare image optimization worker)
# This is the deployed image-cdn worker URL
VITE_IMAGE_CDN_URL=https://image-cdn.vac811.workers.dev

# ─── Gallery Curation Budgets & Tuning ───────────────────────────────────────

# Token budgets for AI scoring (limits cost)
# Preflight uses gpt-4o-mini tokens; Haiku uses claude-haiku tokens
GALLERY_PREFLIGHT_BUDGET=600
GALLERY_HAIKU_BUDGET=600

# API rate limiting (ms between requests to avoid throttling)
GALLERY_PREFLIGHT_INTERVAL_MS=1100

# ─── Optional: Advanced Gallery Configuration ────────────────────────────────
# These have sensible defaults in the workflows if not provided

# Comma-separated years to process (e.g., "2026,2025,2024")
# GALLERY_YEARS=

# Model for main scoring (defaults to claude-opus-4-8)
# GALLERY_MODEL=

# Primary event keywords (defaults to "tábor,camp")
# GALLERY_PRIMARY_KEYWORDS=

# Concurrency for Drive folder scanning
# GALLERY_CONCURRENCY=

# Deduplication distance (perceptual hash similarity threshold, 0-64)
# GALLERY_DEDUP_DISTANCE=

# Max photos per minor event
# GALLERY_MAX_PER_EVENT=1

# Max photos from primary (tábor) event per year
# GALLERY_MAX_PRIMARY_EVENT=12

# Min score for minor event photos (0–100)
# GALLERY_MINOR_THRESHOLD=80

# Min score for primary event photos (0–100)
# GALLERY_SCORE_THRESHOLD=50

# Dry-run mode (list without writing)
# GALLERY_DRY_RUN=false
